<section id="fiction">
<header id="fiction-header">
<img src="//i.imgur.com/Z1nHRpP.jpg" class="cover"/>
<h1 class="fiction-title">Realm Eternal</h1>
<span class="add-to-list"><a class="add-button">Add to list</a>
<div class="list-options" fid="773">
<a class="follow"><i>&#xf02e;</i>Follow</a>
<a class="to-read"><i>&#xf00b;</i>Read it later</a>
<a class="fav"><i>&#xf005;</i>Favorite</a>
<a class="recommend"><i>&#xf0c0;</i>Recommend</a>
</div>
</span><span class="author">by nBosega</span>
<div class="description"><p>Meet Nabi Elrick ; betrayed by the woman he loves, and blinded by anger he acts rashly and it nearly costs him everything. Nabi Elrick’s actions have drastic consequences and he looses the prestige of his occupation and he sinks into an epic slump; a Deep depression. Fortunately the Alternate Reality Simulation Realm Eternal rouses him from his melancholic abyss.</p>
<p>Nabi Elrick sees an opportunity to Begin Again.</p>
<p>Inspired by; Mushoku Tensei, Tate no Yuusha no Nariagari, Legendary Moonlight Sculptor, Daybreak on Hyperion, Log Horizon and Only Sense Online. I unashamedly draw some elements from my favourite light novels in writing this FanFic.</p>
<p>For the Record; the Realm Eternal Mythology Revolves Around Ancient Dragons</p>
<p>My Chapter target is set at 5000 words. </p>
<p>Warning: Mature Content – Violence, Language &#038; Adult Themes </p>
<p style="margin-top: 10px">Categories: Action , Adventure , Drama , Fantasy , Martial Arts , Mature , Romance , Sci-Fi , Virtual Reality , Original , </p></div>
</header>
